 * <li><b>incancompare </b>optional, boolean value, true to group comparison (false by default). Disabled if nbgroups is greater than bwf_groupCanCompareThreshold</li>
 * <li><b>incanshowdetails </b>optional, boolean value, true to enable button to show details (false by default)</li>
